1
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:30,270
=Fights Break Sphere=

2
00:01:40,270 --> 00:01:42,840
=Episode 36=

3
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:41,140
Flame-Splitting Wave-Devouring Ruler!

4
00:03:49,270 --> 00:03:51,200
Didn’t I tell you

5
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:54,420
not to use other Fight Techniques?

6
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:58,380
The Fight Techniques of those
other dissenting unorthdox sects,

7
00:03:58,380 --> 00:04:01,000
how can they be useful to you?

8
00:04:05,270 --> 00:04:07,750
The ability to defeat you
is a good Fight Technique.

9
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:09,910
Idiot!

10
00:04:11,170 --> 00:04:15,400
The best Fight Technique in all the world
is precisely the Fight Techniques of our Xiao family.

11
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,670
What is the Star Fall Pavilion regarded as?

12
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:22,650
I’ve learned over 140 types
of their Heaven Rank Fight Techniques.

13
00:04:22,650 --> 00:04:25,000
They're full of mistakes.

14
00:04:25,610 --> 00:04:29,020
I've learned the Thirteen Sword Skills
of the Cloud Mist Sect, too.

15
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:31,970
They don't distinguish any degree of seriousness.

16
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:35,090
The Heaven Rank
Fight Techniques of the Nalan family

17
00:04:35,090 --> 00:04:39,380
only have twenty types.
Those Fight Techniques are like barbaric bulls.

18
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:41,920
They’re simply not worth mentioning.

19
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:47,730
In those days, I used fist against fist
and sword against sword,

20
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:51,430
beating all of them until they admitted defeat.

21
00:04:53,470 --> 00:04:56,060
What kind of Fight Techniques
belong to Soul Hall?

22
00:04:56,060 --> 00:04:57,980
They're all based on evil ways.

23
00:04:57,980 --> 00:05:02,160
The Fight Techniques of the Blood Sect
are purely witchcraft.

24
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:05,980
The Fight Techniques of the Gu Clan...
don't even mention them.

25
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:11,140
Relying on rough skin and thick flesh
and being good at soaring to the Ninth Heaven.

26
00:05:11,140 --> 00:05:15,510
As long as you can change their Fight Qi into wings,

27
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:17,770
they shouldn’t be surprising either.

28
00:05:17,770 --> 00:05:21,890
As for the Snake Tribe and the Demon Phoenix Clan,

29
00:05:21,890 --> 00:05:25,420
they're nothing more than insignificant and minor skills.

30
00:05:25,420 --> 00:05:27,730
You’ve learned all those Fight Techniques?

31
00:05:30,530 --> 00:05:34,030
I’ve been obsessed with practicing cultivation
and refinement my whole life.

32
00:05:34,030 --> 00:05:36,980
There are very few that I haven’t learned.

33
00:05:37,490 --> 00:05:39,770
Then what about these inside
Fight Technique Pavillion?

34
00:05:40,930 --> 00:05:43,300
I’ve learned all of them, too.

35
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:47,010
When I have time, I’ll make a few changes

36
00:05:47,010 --> 00:05:49,580
to fill in some of the gaps.

37
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:55,820
Ancestor, regard it as me begging you.
Will you let me go out, all right?

38
00:05:55,820 --> 00:05:59,630
My family and friends are all facing threats from Soul Hall.

39
00:05:59,630 --> 00:06:02,780
I... I really can’t stay in here and continue
to practice cultivation and refinement.

40
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:05,360
How about this? You let me go out first.

41
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:07,820
Wait until I save my sister and make proper arrangements
for my family and friends.

42
00:06:07,820 --> 00:06:11,710
Then, I’ll come back in for you. It’ll be fine
for you to say how many years. All right?

43
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:14,050
Good-for-nothing.

44
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:24,590
A Fight Practitioner can only make friends
with Fight Techniques.

45
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:31,310
- Do you really think so?
- Of course.

46
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:35,560
Friends and other families,
I have had them all.

47
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,700
But of what use are those anyway?

48
00:06:37,700 --> 00:06:42,500
In those days, I rode with the Fight God
to fight the world and saw so many heroes.

49
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:44,850
But where are they all now?

50
00:06:44,850 --> 00:06:48,240
Furthermore, my family and children

51
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:52,520
multiplied from generation to generation.
What are they doing now?

52
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:57,080
- Who cares about what I’m doing?
- You really don’t care at all about the outside world?

53
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,190
You don’t care at all?

54
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:02,220
The outside world is all your world.

55
00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:06,740
My world is only in here.

56
00:07:08,050 --> 00:07:10,280
When I was forty years old,

57
00:07:13,010 --> 00:07:15,070
I was buried in here by our people.

58
00:07:17,130 --> 00:07:21,270
For thousands of years,
I've concentrated on practicing Fight Techniques.

59
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:25,230
There isn’t one day that I feel tired and bored.

60
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:27,320
People will die

61
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:31,890
and also leave, but the Fight Techniques will not.

62
00:07:32,940 --> 00:07:37,040
The Fight Qi that you’ve learned will forever be your own.

63
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:44,020
It’s only fine if you inherit my ideals.

64
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:47,910
I can’t inherit your ideals. I’m not you.

65
00:07:50,570 --> 00:07:53,740
After all, what’s so good about the outside world?

66
00:07:54,630 --> 00:07:58,900
Is there anything in the world that’s more meaningful
than practicing cultivation and refinement?

67
00:08:01,970 --> 00:08:05,770
Anyway, I’m not learning anymore.
Why don’t you just beat me to death, all right?

68
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:12,960
In the Fight Qi Continent,

69
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:17,300
how many people are ecstatic to have just one type of Fight
Techniques to settle down with and continue their pursuit?

70
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:21,800
Once a teacher is found, the person will vow to
follow the teacher for life and never leave.

71
00:08:22,590 --> 00:08:25,200
You have so many Fight Techniques now

72
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:27,000
and a teacher like me, too.

73
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,480
Yet, you still want to go outside.

74
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,950
Are you crazy?!

75
00:08:32,540 --> 00:08:37,750
I’m not crazy. It’s just that I have something
I care more about. That’s all.

76
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:41,990
Ancestor, we have no way of persuading each other.

77
00:08:41,990 --> 00:08:44,900
Let me go out, all right?
Don’t keep me here anymore.

78
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:47,580
Say that again.

79
00:08:47,580 --> 00:08:51,080
Believe it or not, I’ll kill you with one strike
and make Xiao Zhan deliver another person to enter!

80
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:53,770
- Hit me, okay?
- You!

81
00:09:03,390 --> 00:09:05,520
I’ve never wanted to be number one in the world.

82
00:09:06,970 --> 00:09:11,430
If this world is peaceful...

83
00:09:11,430 --> 00:09:17,490
If there's no hatred from my mother death or a three-year
pact and the people by my side are safe and sound...

84
00:09:17,490 --> 00:09:19,340
I wish I could...

85
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:22,860
I wish I could make me a person
not having any Fight Qi.

86
00:09:23,450 --> 00:09:25,130
That way...

87
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:29,160
That way I can just be together
with my friends every day,

88
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:34,020
be with my family every day,
and be together with the people I like.

89
00:09:38,430 --> 00:09:42,070
I’ve never wanted to succeed in learning like you.

90
00:09:42,070 --> 00:09:45,290
Even more so, I don’t want a lifetime
filled with Fight Techniques.

91
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:52,720
If you disapprove, just kill me. Okay?

92
00:09:53,970 --> 00:09:58,440
For each day I’m in here,
I’ll definitely think of a way to get out.

93
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:00,530
You dare?!

94
00:10:01,890 --> 00:10:04,520
This is my place.

95
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:07,310
You must follow my rules.

96
00:10:07,310 --> 00:10:11,460
There are still fourteen days.
If you can’t beat me,

97
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:14,090
I’ll personally feed you poison.

98
00:10:16,990 --> 00:10:21,030
You have no motivation.

99
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:34,470
I can’t defeat him.

100
00:10:34,470 --> 00:10:36,770
I can’t argue against him either.

101
00:10:36,770 --> 00:10:41,230
This Ancestor is even more difficult
to handle than Soul Hall.

102
00:10:41,230 --> 00:10:44,120
There are still fourteen days.
You still have a chance.

103
00:10:45,710 --> 00:10:51,040
Medicine Elder, are you still hiding some kind
of Star Fall Pavilion unique scroll?

104
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:55,510
I just know that during this critical moment,
I still must depend on you.

105
00:10:58,210 --> 00:11:00,000
You haven’t understood my meaning.

106
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:04,450
I meant that you still have fourteen days,
that's 168 hours.

107
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:12,080
Medicine Elder, could it be that
even you don’t have a solution?

108
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:16,780
It’s also not bad to stay in here with me.
At least you can survive.

109
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:20,260
It’s really a good place to be during chaotic times.

110
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:26,360
It’s not like that. I came to this place

111
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:30,510
in order to find my own answers,
not to stay in here.

112
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:40,500
Medicine Elder, it’s critical that I create
a Fight Technique that belongs only to me in here.

113
00:11:43,900 --> 00:11:45,800
What's the difference?

114
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:49,400
I need a Fight Technique that’s very powerful.

115
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:52,600
Powerful enough to upend Heaven and Earth
at a critical moment.

116
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:55,200
Powerful enough to change the world.

117
00:11:58,200 --> 00:12:01,800
Xun’er, my father,
my big brother, and second brother.

118
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:04,800
Also, Little Medicine Fairy, Medusa,
the Snake People Empire, and Lin Xiuya. All them...

119
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,800
All those that are still outside.

120
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:09,000
All those who are waiting for me to come out.

121
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:12,400
But if you go out, you’ll lose everything,
all the Fight Techniques.

122
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:14,600
Won’t you regret it?

123
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,400
No matter how powerful the Fight Techniques are,

124
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:18,600
they’re also only worldly possessions.

125
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:21,000
But family and friends are not.

126
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,400
Once they are lost,

127
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:25,600
they won't come back anymore.

128
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:35,700
Your mother said the same words to me, too.

129
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:38,800
Really?

130
00:12:39,590 --> 00:12:42,150
Then I’ll regard it
as I haven’t humiliated my mother either.

131
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,800
I'm going out.

132
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,800
Don’t use outdated styles.

133
00:13:02,100 --> 00:13:04,100
This move is too stiff.

134
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:09,800
What kind of Fight Techniques are you learning?

135
00:13:14,300 --> 00:13:15,700
Get up.

136
00:13:17,010 --> 00:13:19,650
You still have ten days.

137
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:34,700
Keep this with you.

138
00:14:40,050 --> 00:14:43,510
Seeing it is just like seeing me.

139
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:03,400
Xun'er, what should I do?

140
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:05,400
It’ll be dark soon.
They still haven’t launched an attack.

141
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:07,600
It seems there won’t be
any fighting today to settle things.

142
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,600
Don’t you understand them?

143
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:14,500
They said before dark.
Then, it’ll definitely be before dark.

144
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:21,800
The people like the West Dragon Master won’t lie.

145
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:24,800
The three islands are pressuring us together.

146
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:28,800
Even if I’m a piece of rock,
I’ll smash their teeth to pieces, too.

147
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:32,800
Xun’er... she hasn’t returned yet?

148
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:34,600
Not yet.

149
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:37,000
Why didn't you let us go out together with Xun’er?

150
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:40,800
A girl like her wanting to find Dragon Mother?
It’s simply a fantasy.

151
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:43,600
This Third Brother is thinking
that we’re going to die.

152
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:47,600
He’s let his own daughter
go out first to escape trouble. Right?

153
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:49,800
Don’t argue anymore!

154
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:57,100
Don’t mention whether Dragon Mother is now
at Thunder and Lightning Valley or not.

155
00:16:57,840 --> 00:17:00,400
Even if Dragon Mother really returns,

156
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:03,400
she’ll blame us for not doing our best
to guard and protect her, too.

157
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:07,500
The Gu Clan brothers are slaughtering each other.

158
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,430
It’s my fault.

159
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,900
That's right.

160
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,500
Who is it?

161
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:23,200
It's that person.

162
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,600
Who is it?

163
00:17:30,800 --> 00:17:33,590
- You are...
- I'm Blood Sect's Fan Lao,

164
00:17:33,590 --> 00:17:36,790
a subordinate of Lord Hun Miesheng.

165
00:17:36,800 --> 00:17:39,600
Since East Dragon Master doesn’t want
a massacre of each other,

166
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:42,800
I think we can have a discussion.

167
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,800
The evil disciple of Soul Hall.

168
00:17:49,800 --> 00:17:53,800
It was you who bewitched our Gu Clan brothers
to cause internal chaos.

169
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:23,000
Our East Dragon Island will not surrender to Soul Hall.

170
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:26,300
If you attack the city, just attack the city.
We swear to fight to the death!

171
00:18:26,300 --> 00:18:30,000
Are all you still believing in a beautiful dream
that Dragon Mother will return?

172
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,600
That’s Dragon Mother’s life pearl.

173
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:42,400
That's right.

174
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:47,200
I used the Soul Hall’s secret technique to seal her off
in the Thunder and Lightning valley.

175
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:50,600
Without her life pearl, she can’t come back.

176
00:18:50,600 --> 00:18:53,800
Your daughter still can’t pass through the valley.

177
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:56,500
It's a hopeless situation.

178
00:18:57,600 --> 00:19:01,000
But it’s not impossible to solve either.

179
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,800
The three island masters have drunk my blood

180
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:06,400
and vowed their loyalty and devotion to Soul Hall.

181
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:09,500
Now there’s only you left.

182
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:12,400
There’s an ancient teaching within our clan.

183
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:15,200
Don’t deal with the people of Soul Hall.

184
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:17,000
I’m going out now.

185
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:20,100
They will attack in three hours.

186
00:19:20,100 --> 00:19:24,200
After all, you know how many soldiers you still have.

187
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:26,600
How long can you last?

188
00:19:26,600 --> 00:19:30,800
At worst, I’ll just establish another Dragon Master.

189
00:19:34,430 --> 00:19:35,890
Wait a moment!

190
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:41,000
Father, what are you doing?

191
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:51,600
If I drink your blood, will you withdraw the soldiers?

192
00:19:51,600 --> 00:19:56,400
The civilians and soldiers of the East Dragon Island
will not die?

193
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:57,600
Of course.

194
00:19:57,600 --> 00:20:01,600
Lord Hun Miesheng is very merciful.

195
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:05,100
Father, don’t believe his lies.

196
00:20:05,100 --> 00:20:09,800
If he wanted to be merciful,
how could my sister die?

197
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:19,600
Father! What are you doing? You absolutely can’t!

198
00:20:22,600 --> 00:20:25,800
The 63rd Dragon Master of East Dragon Island,

199
00:20:25,800 --> 00:20:30,300
Gu's later generation, Gu Xia, wishes to vow
loyalty and devotion to Lord Hun Miesheng.

200
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:33,100
The world...

201
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:37,600
Is it the world of Soul Hall or the Five Clans?

202
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:03,400
I thank you, Lord Fan Lao,
for bestowing your blood.

203
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:07,400
Good. In the future, the Gu Clan
will be subordinates of the Soul Hall.

204
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:10,800
Everyone must obey the instructions of Lord Hun Miesheng.

205
00:21:10,800 --> 00:21:15,000
Since you’ve drunk my blood,
you’ll be connected with my thoughts.

206
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:17,600
Don’t use anything to play dirty tricks.

207
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:22,600
Yes. All levels of Gu Clan will only obey
the commands of Lord Hun Miesheng.

208
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:23,400
Father.

209
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:26,600
Tidy up then.
Prepare to open the city gates and extend greetings.

210
00:21:26,600 --> 00:21:29,200
The Four Islands Dragon Masters will feast

211
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:32,200
to celebrate the Gu Clan uniting
and seeking refuge to the next master.

212
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:36,400
Yes. I will definitely tidy the city

213
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:40,200
and wait respectfully for Lord Fan Lao
and the three Dragon Masters.

214
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:27,120
You're awake?

215
00:22:29,910 --> 00:22:31,550
Dragon Mother.

216
00:22:40,520 --> 00:22:43,580
Dragon Mother, I’ve finally found you.

217
00:22:43,580 --> 00:22:46,920
Do you know that the Gu Clan is now suffering
from the influence of Soul Hall.

218
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:48,700
They're attacking each other now.

219
00:22:48,700 --> 00:22:52,120
Quickly follow me back
and manage the current situation, all right?

220
00:22:52,120 --> 00:22:54,930
You’ve truly overestimated your capabilities.

221
00:22:54,930 --> 00:22:57,890
You dared to intrude
into Thunder and Lightning Valley.

222
00:22:57,890 --> 00:23:03,070
If it weren't for me saving you just now,
you would’ve died already. Do you know that?

223
00:23:08,190 --> 00:23:15,130
If I remember correctly, you were sent to
that Xiao family when you were young.

224
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:17,310
Yes.

225
00:23:17,310 --> 00:23:19,940
Then why aren’t you properly
staying with the Xiao family?

226
00:23:19,940 --> 00:23:21,930
The East Dragon Island has a problem.

227
00:23:21,930 --> 00:23:25,390
It was my father, Gu Yuan, who brought me back.

228
00:23:25,390 --> 00:23:28,080
The Gu Clan is now being influenced
by the Soul Hall’s power.

229
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:31,110
North, South, and West
are using your disappearance as an excuse.

230
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:33,290
They are besieging the East Island now.

231
00:23:33,290 --> 00:23:35,770
Hurry and come back with me, all right?

232
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:45,120
I’m being restricted here by the Soul Hall’s technique.
I'm trapped here

233
00:23:45,890 --> 00:23:48,270
and I've lost my life pearl.

234
00:23:48,270 --> 00:23:50,890
My magical power has been greatly reduced.

235
00:23:50,890 --> 00:23:56,270
I can’t resist the thunder and lightning outside.
I can’t go out.

236
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:58,400
Then what should be done?

237
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:05,030
I can’t go out, but you can.

238
00:24:06,800 --> 00:24:11,190
I came to take you out.
What’s the use of me going out alone?

239
